description: RecipeHub code style, copy tone, and README feature notes
alwaysApply: true
---

# Code style

- Do not exceed more than 200 lines of code in any React component file. If it exceeds, create a new component and import it.
- Do not use inline CSS styling (use CSS files or shared tokens).
- Use a casual tone for any user-facing text. Do not use em dashes.

# Documentation

- When a new feature is added, add a short note under the Features section in `README.md`.
